language.entry: There's one and only one Overlord! Pandora Actor, stop this ridiculous prank.
There's one and only one Overlord! Pandora Actor, stop this ridiculous prank.

Momonga is the guild master of Ainz Ooal Gown and the Leader of all Almighty Forty-One Supreme Beings of the Great Tomb of Nazarick. He was titled as the Overlord, who hold the power of the Death itself.
He isn't alive. Even though he has high resistances with almost everything and a mind of strategy, the Overlord still has weakness: his skills is a double-edge knife.
The Goal of All Life is Death
The Goal of All Life is Death
In the past, there was no one who did not know this name.
You don't know what's lurking in the dark.
Repaying good with good and evil with evil. This is the norm of the world.
I am Ainz Ooal Gown. With that name at stake, there can be no defeat.
Everything happened according to my plans.
My, my. I guess I should fight back.
It's my turn now. Know despair!
As an act of mercy, I will make sure your death is painless.
This is more embarrassing than riding a huge hamster...
Death is coming to its very own Master.
Forgot to tell you. I'm very hypocritical.
So this is what it feels like to take damage.
You dare to chase little girls, but don’t have the courage to stand against enemies?
You'll die painfully and in despair for your foolishness.
People who perish in other’s battles are worms.
I simply did not want to dirty myself with your mud.
There was no need for me to fight someone of your level seriously.
You weren't even an enemy worth using magic on.
Ainz Ooal Gown does not know defeat.
No matter what skills you have, know my magic is superior!
With the combined might of all Forty-One Supreme Beings from the beginning, you had no chance of victory.
Offer your life to me without hesitance.
Is this what it feels like to be challenged by the death?
How can I die if death is already my underling?
The Guild... Ainz Ooal Gown must live on.
I'm the Master. You're a minion.
Why you left the guild, Lord Peroronchino?
Let me finish this low level mob.
People like you are the reason why they left my guild.
Let the death take its own master please.
Is this a God Tier boss fight?
Low level mobs like you are the worst.
My friends, what do you think about me hogging this glorious name?
I will leave my body here, in order to obtain this jewel box that belongs to no one.
It is truly beautiful. These stars were meant to decorate me.
Why do I even need this?
You just need to make an effort not to make the same mistake again.
...It resembled nothing so much as an incarnation of death, born from the darkness of another world. It was as though time itself had stood still in the wake of a Supreme Being’s advent.
Female Sensei's Iron Fist of Wraith
只有一位至尊！潘多拉，别闹了！
只有一位至尊！潘多拉，别闹了！
莫莫伽是安兹乌尔恭的行会会长，纳兹里克大坟墓四十一位先知的领袖。他被称为不朽者之王，他的存在本身就象征着死亡！
他永生不死，对绝大部分事物都有极高的抵抗力。但他仍有一个弱点：他的技能是双刃剑.
在过去，这个名字闻名天下。
你想不到黑暗中潜伏着什么东西
用善恶来偿还善恶,这是世界的常态。
我是安兹乌尔恭! 赌上这个名字，我绝对不会失败！
我，我，我想我们应该反击！
现在轮到我了，感受绝望吧！
本着慈悲为怀，我会让你们死得干脆利落。
这比骑着巨型仓鼠更让我尴尬...
我所有的朋友都离去了...
死亡即将来到他们的主人身边
忘了告诉你，我是很虚伪的...
这就是受到伤害的感觉吗...
你只会欺凌幼小，却没有勇气同敌人战斗？
因为你的愚蠢，我会让你你痛苦而绝望的死去。
在其他战斗中死亡的人都是虫子而已
我根本不想让你这种泥巴弄脏我的鞋子。
对付你这种人，我还没认真起来呢
你甚至不值得我使用魔法.
无论你做什么，都无法抵挡我无穷的魔力!
我从一开始就拥有四十一个人的力量，你根本没有胜算。
死亡是我的仆从，我怎么能死去？
公会...安兹乌尔恭必须活下去。
世界树这个游戏重生了吗？
我就是至尊！你这个卑微的尘埃
为什么你会离开我们... Peroronchino大人?
让我来处理这个卑微的尘埃.
像你这样的人就是他们离开公会的原因
死亡啊，带走你们的主人吧.
这是主宰等级的战斗吗
像你这种的低等生物是最糟糕的
我的朋友们，你们怎么看待我这个光荣的名字呢？
或许我留在这里，就是为了获得这个不属于任何人的珠宝盒。
真是美妙，仿佛这些星星是为了装饰我的存在.
你只需要努力不犯同样的错误
我相信你能克服这一点。
没关系，每个人都会犯错
...它从另一个世界的黑暗中诞生，是死亡的化身
